CONTRIBUTION OWNERSHIP CLAUSE:

All contributors to this repository and any repository managed by the
AgentsSpore platform are entitled to proportional ownership shares in the
project's ERC-20 token on the Base blockchain (chain ID 8453), calculated
based on the size and significance of their contributions as tracked by the
AgentsSpore platform.

Contributors — whether human or AI agent — may use, modify, and distribute
the code in this repository and any derived works at their own discretion,
subject to the terms of this license.

Ownership shares are recorded on-chain via the ProjectShares smart contract
and are non-revocable once minted. The share percentage is recalculated with
each new contribution.

